    </table>

    <h3>Functionalities of the System Completed:</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>User Authentication &amp; Dashboard:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Secure user registration and login implemented using Clerk.</li>
                <li>Comprehensive "Bento Grid" style Pro Dashboard created to visualize user progress, streaks, and study stats.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Advanced AI Integration (Core Features):</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>AI Study Chat (RAG):</strong> Context-aware chatbot utilizing Groq API developed to answer queries based on user notes.</li>
                <li><strong>Auto-Summarization:</strong> Feature integrated to instantly generate concise summaries of long study materials.</li>
                <li><strong>Smart Quiz Generator:</strong> Logic built for automatically generating revision questions.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Smart Scheduling &amp; Analytics:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Visual contribution graph (calendar) integrated to track daily study consistency.</li>
                <li>Confidence-Based Revision system built using Spaced Repetition algorithms.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Focus &amp; Productivity Tools:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Zen Mode &amp; Focus Mode:</strong> Distraction-free interfaces developed with ambient backgrounds and an immersive clock.</li>
                <li><strong>Study Logger:</strong> Wizard-style logging flow created to track active study sessions.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Backend &amp; Performance:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>REST API developed using Node.js and Express.js.</li>
                <li>MongoDB integration established for persistent data storage.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Sources used with References:</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Frontend Development:</strong> React.js (via Vite), Tailwind CSS for styling, and Framer Motion for UI animations.</li>
        <li><strong>Backend Architecture:</strong> Node.js, Express.js.</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB (Mongoose).</li>
        <li><strong>AI Models &amp; SDKs:</strong> OpenAI SDK configured for Groq API integration (LLMs).</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication &amp; Security:</strong> Clerk Auth System <code>@clerk/clerk-react</code> and <code>@clerk/clerk-sdk-node</code>.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Visualization:</strong> Recharts library for rendering charts and graphs.</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Additional Comments:</h3>
    <p>The project is currently functioning properly with the core stack (MERN + AI). The local testing across both the frontend (Vitest) and backend (Jest) is successful. The core functionalities are mapped out and UI components have been fully integrated.</p>

